---
title: Things I've Made
layout: page
---
<ul>
  <% data.projects.each do |project| %>
    <li>
      <h3><%= project.name %></h3>
      <% if project.description %>
        <p><%= project.description %></p>
      <% end %>
      <% if project.github %>
        <div>
          View the code on <a href="https://github.com/<%= project.github %>" target="_blank">GitHub</a>.
        </div>
      <% end %>
      <% if project.live_link %>
        <div>
          View it live <a href="https://github.com/<%= project.live_link %>" target="_blank">here</a>.
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </li>
  <% end %>
</ul>
<hr>
<p>
  That's just a handful of favourites. I've got loads more projects that be
  found on my <a href="https://github.com/lpil" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
  account. Feel free to have a look.
</p>
